description: The UBC Event Collection Application is designed to gather the comprehensive information of an event in the UBC community. It aims to simplify the process of tracking the event-related data. To achieve the goals mentioned above, the database will include the following entities: Event, Organizer, Staff, Location, Photo, Participant, Feedback, Sponsor. Each of these entities has crucial information regarding the event, thus ensuring that the application effectively collects and stores all the essential data.
